<li><strong>Ipecacuanha:</strong> For <a class="wpil_keyword_link" href="https://weclinic.in/blog/how-to-treat-nausea-with-homeopathy"   title="nausea" data-wpil-keyword-link="linked"  data-wpil-monitor-id="2514">nausea</a> or vomiting caused by severe coughing.</li>
