<p>Whooping cough in adults can be less severe than in children but still causes significant discomfort and fatigue. Homeopathy may help by focusing on symptom relief and improving energy levels. Adults are less likely to experience severe complications but should still ensure proper medical evaluation to rule out secondary infections or prolonged recovery.</p>



